"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/856067","Ministry of Justice","false","2018-03-14","<p>The on-site Silver command suite at HMP Bedford has been opened five times since 1 January 2018 to deal with local incidents. The National Gold command suite has not been opened to deal with any incidents at HMP Bedford in this period.</p>","Penrith and The Border","Rory Stewart",,"2018-03-14T17:05:40.803Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/856067/answer","Biography information for Rory Stewart","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/856067/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/856067/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2018-03-06","Bedford Prison","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many times the command suite has been opened at HMP Bedford since 1 January 2018.","false","Biography information for Richard Burgon","Leeds East","Richard Burgon","131233"
